    <div class="bg-center bg-cover" data-bgimg-srcset="/content/dam/canada/1x1.png 991w, /content/dam/cirnac-rcaanc/images/header_image6c.png 992w">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-7">
				<h1 property="name" id="wb-cont">Crown-Indigenous Relations and Northern Affairs Canada</h1>
				<p>Crown-Indigenous Relations and Northern Affairs Canada (CIRNAC) continues to renew the nation-to-nation, Inuit-Crown, government-to-government relationship between Canada and First Nations, Inuit and Métis; modernize Government of Canada structures to enable Indigenous peoples to build capacity and support their vision of self-determination and lead the Government of Canada's work in the North.</p>
				<!-- <p><a class="btn btn-call-to-action" href="#">Supertask button</a></p> -->
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
